ask Dobby to marry me for a couple
of weeks.

17:17.494 --> 17:20.013
OK. Deal?

17:20.015 --> 17:21.773
Deal.

17:21.775 --> 17:25.773
'Two weeks to find the nicest
ring for under £200.'

17:27.454 --> 17:31.454
