- Yeah, I know. The thing is,
I don't trust you.

17:46.735 --> 17:48.774
What if I say you can't?

17:48.775 --> 17:52.774
If you say that, I might be forced
to say something too.

17:53.015 --> 17:54.294
Hey, Dobs.

17:54.295 --> 17:55.974
Hey, Jez.

17:55.975 --> 17:59.974
