weekend.

18:01.215 --> 18:02.454
Hope you don't mind.

18:02.455 --> 18:05.214
Oh, no, that's... totally fine.

18:05.215 --> 18:08.654
Don't mind me. I'll just be hanging
out, staying close to my buddy here.

18:08.655 --> 18:10.774
Cos we look after each other.

18:10.775 --> 18:13.054
You watch my back, I watch yours.

18:13.055 --> 18:17.054
Isn't that right, dude?

18:18.015 --> 18:19.694
What's going on, Mark?

18:19.695 --> 18:22.054
I'm really sorry,
but I had to bring him.

18:22.055 --> 18:25.134
It turns out there's something
I need to tell you about Jeremy.

18:25.135 --> 18:27.374
I should have told you
a long time ago

18:27.375 --> 18:30.254
but there's a reason why
he's such a dickhead.

18:30.255 --> 18:33.014
Yeah?
It's ironic with the life coaching,

18:33.015 --> 18:34.894
but it turns out he's a drug addict.

18:34.895 --> 18:38.614
I won't be long!
I'll be very quick!

18:38.615 --> 18:40.134
Right, OK.

18:40.135 --> 18:44.134
Also, he can't get an erection
unless he thinks about
something... disgusting.

18:44.615 --> 18:46.774
I don't want to say what.

18:46.775 --> 18:50.134
Plus he thinks he might be gay.
He's 80% certain.

18:50.135 --> 18:52.534
'80, nice. No need to overdo it.'

18:52.535 --> 18:55.574
So he's dealing with that,
which I think is great,

18:55.575 --> 18:57.614
and I'm being very supportive over.

18:57.615 --> 19:01.614
I always thought he might be
a bit gay, but more like 30%,
if I'm honest.

19:01.735 --> 19:03.334
He's incredibly unstable.

19:03.335 --> 19:07.334
So it was either bring him along or
risk getting home to find him, you
know...

19:09.775 --> 19:11.254
Yeah.

19:11.255 --> 19:13.894
Right. It's just...
our special weekend away?

19:13.895 --> 19:15.494
'Change the subject.'

19:15.495 --> 19:16.734
One sugar, Jez?

19:16.735 --> 19:18.614
Yes, please.

19:18.615 --> 19:21.894
I gave him one without sugar the
other day and he got really angry
with himself

19:21.895 --> 19:24.574
and smashed up a CD case
and tried to eat the pieces.

19:24.575 --> 19:27.814
'He'd better not have bloody
said anything or there will be
repercussions.

19:27.815 --> 19:29.694
'Extremely romantic repercussions.'

19:29.695 --> 19:31.254
So...

19:31.255 --> 19:32.574
did I miss anything?

19:32.575 --> 19:33.934
I had half a Scotch egg.

19:33.935 --> 19:35.294
Brilliant.

19:35.295 --> 19:37.974
'I need a wee too,
but I will continue resisting.

19:37.975 --> 19:41.214
'My bladder is not so easily
the master of me, young Jedi.'

19:41.215 --> 19:42.534
Pie, Mark?

19:42.535 --> 19:45.494
No, I'm fine, thanks, Dobs,
but I'll cut you a slice.

19:45.495 --> 19:47.214
'He doesn't want any delicious pie?

19:47.215 --> 19:49.574
'Normally he loves pie. Suspicious.

19:49.575 --> 19:50.854
'Very suspicious.

19:50.855 --> 19:53.974
'He did spend a long time in the
kitchen preparing the picnic.

19:53.975 --> 19:55.254
'Of course! A ring!

19:55.255 --> 19:58.094
