engagement ring into the pie!'

19:58.095 --> 20:02.094
Sorry, Dobs, just need to check
something.

20:02.815 --> 20:04.254
What the hell are you doing?

20:04.255 --> 20:06.534
I'm wise to you,
my fine, feathered friend.

20:06.535 --> 20:10.534
