Now to stigmatise the mentally ill.'

20:11.375 --> 20:13.174
Apologies. All good.

20:13.175 --> 20:15.014
Great picnic, though, Dobs.

20:15.015 --> 20:18.254
Yeah, it's just a shame Jeremy
put too many olives in the salad.

20:18.255 --> 20:20.014
No, I bloody didn't.

20:20.015 --> 20:22.934
