because you already broke it!

21:41.295 --> 21:42.694
Oh, fuck you!

21:42.695 --> 21:43.734
Dobby!

21:43.735 --> 21:45.574
No, Jeremy! Dobby!

21:47.455 --> 21:49.494
What the hell are you doing?

21:49.495 --> 21:53.374
That fence is electrified
