21:53.375 --> 21:54.614
No, Jeremy.

21:54.615 --> 21:56.214
What?
I know what you're thinking.

21:56.215 --> 21:59.334
Oh, really?
Is this about the bloody olives?

21:59.335 --> 22:01.534
No, Dobby.
It's about something else.

22:01.535 --> 22:03.494
Aaagh!

22:03.495 --> 22:05.014
