22:05.015 --> 22:08.294
Because, Dobby, there's something
I need to say to... Aagh! Ow!

22:08.295 --> 22:10.534
Will you stop electrocuting
each other?

22:10.535 --> 22:13.054
Hi, Simon.

22:13.055 --> 22:15.294
'What's a step up from electric?

22:15.295 --> 22:16.734
'A nice big stick.'

22:16.735 --> 22:19.014
Oh, we're allowed sticks now,
