22:19.015 --> 22:21.494
It's come down to sticks.
Is that what it's come down to?

22:21.495 --> 22:22.654
As a matter of fact, it has.

22:22.655 --> 22:24.934
Well, how about rocks?

22:24.935 --> 22:27.174
Are rocks invited to the party?

22:27.175 --> 22:29.894
