22:29.895 --> 22:31.734
Yeah, you'd love that, wouldn't you?

22:31.735 --> 22:34.054
"Dobby, the bad man threw
a rock at me."

22:34.055 --> 22:37.334
Mark, if you don't throw that rock at
me, I'm going to hit you with this
stick.

22:37.335 --> 22:39.574
Those are the available options.

22:39.575 --> 22:42.214
Oh, my God, she's gone.
Where's she gone?

22:42.215 --> 22:44.494
Yeah, good one.
Distract me, then crush my skull.

22:44.495 --> 22:46.294
I'm not falling for that one,
old friend.

22:46.295 --> 22:48.094
Dobby?

22:48.095 --> 22:49.294
Dobby!

22:49.295 --> 22:50.854
'Fucking hell!'

22:50.855 --> 22:52.454
Shit.

22:52.455 --> 22:55.494
See? She's gone.
