22:55.495 --> 22:57.134
Ow!

22:57.135 --> 22:58.974
You were asking for that, Jez.

22:58.975 --> 23:01.174
Don't tell me you weren't,
because you know you were!

23:01.175 --> 23:02.494
Dobby!

23:02.495 --> 23:05.134
Please be Dobby.

23:05.135 --> 23:07.134
Oh, fuck. What?

23:07.135 --> 23:09.694
